{"tid":1607710,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大Ｊ：【緊急】就算被扣上手扣都能用！iOS shortcut保命！","createTime":"2019-10-01T03:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T13:11:19.000Z","uid":114802,"like":294,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"4e1c5a7c1138e72d97bf755b393fbc2a2ec4560c","tid":1607710,"uid":114802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:09:58.000Z","msg":"睇片<br />\n適用IOS手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OBF3v5_ouWc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOBF3v5_ouWc&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=d316f768\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OBF3v5_ouWc</a>"},{"pid":"53ec5647b50a9f5549488017e8e200c5663c20a8","tid":1607710,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3bc2461d57e38e20512b5e105e76392d950323","tid":1607710,"uid":15259,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:11:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">六區開花要對準政權，梗係去議員辦事處賀佢老母啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再</span></strong></span>企起街上面<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>圍警局</strong></span></span>，分區活動就應該<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>打游擊戰去搵該區既建制派議員</strong></span></span>同佢地開party一齊賀一賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，至於邊一區去邊間就大家自己衡量下喇﹗<br />\n<br />\n屯門區區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=9246f7ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n荃灣區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=678fdfde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n沙田區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=e1942f20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n黃大仙區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=65a4979b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n深水埗區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=9cb404b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n灣仔區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=2255f57b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話（呢個係每日都可以做既）</span></span></strong><br />\n打電話搵議員(之前有巴打post過出黎，可以自己搵下)問下國慶期間區內有咩最新活動、巴士路線、有咩醫生診所好介紹呀等等，電話打唔通既whatsapp都可以，無whatsapp既巴絲打可以send email去，連email都無既可以fax過去查詢下，無人應既話可以搵下無限fax大法fax到佢應機為止。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2.連儂牆</strong></span></span><br />\n都係搵立法會議員/區議員辦事處啦，無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3.裝修</strong></span></span><br />\n有好多議員都扎根起屋邨做左好耐，裡面啲裝修又殘又舊，有心既手足可以襯國慶幫佢地補下油、翻新下添置返少少國慶節日既氣氛，用咩色就自己決定啦。<br />\n補充:好多office既出入口好窄，大家入office查詢既時候動作唔好太大呀，唔小心撞到佢地d玻璃就大鑊喇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>4.餵office既龜龜食野(蟲系魔法師出動)</strong></span></span><br />\n巴絲打們都可以準備少少紅蟲、蚯蚓、生雞蛋、甜野呀個d比入面既龜龜食，可以吸引到更多蟲蟲輕易大量繁殖既就更好。大家知啦，議員們公事繁忙，萬一無時間餵佢地，龜龜都仲有少少野食丫嘛。<br />\n補充：拉開櫃桶餵既時候記住小心啲，唔好倒瀉手上罐可樂呀，會惹到成地蟻架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>原post:</strong></span><br />\n國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a>"},{"pid":"bd58a524858e1618ff632a9c9d74b7611395fc93","tid":1607710,"uid":114802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:14:21.000Z","msg":"前線手足一定要整！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係至少都整tg scheduled msg！！！！"},{"pid":"94b2650fa14ee82ff398d7419cba6349a83d1b67","tid":1607710,"uid":114802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:15:40.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！"},{"pid":"5704e922829592eed34c4b8830cbe7ed15be710e","tid":1607710,"uid":268160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:20:09.000Z","msg":"Useful"},{"pid":"7952029928b7be127a586d8fa17195501f6b36b1","tid":1607710,"uid":249883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:20:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac1ab1920dddbba369bb340d12a6a9cff6f954ed","tid":1607710,"uid":301989,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:21:13.000Z","msg":"全港第一 youtuber<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a525a11f0bd7096904325e41b735b65629c7fc21","tid":1607710,"uid":114802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d38f720598f0af3287b73d1bc43a2b8bb385e5f","tid":1607710,"uid":114802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:22:54.000Z","msg":"睇片呀，整好先出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59bdd9db044e481dd999f216dd8abca7ca412d4","tid":1607710,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:24:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9b0db3d990a8066b68ac2af19b9a521a23aef08","tid":1607710,"uid":58287,"like":2,"dislike":75,"score":-73,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:26:11.000Z","msg":"話人做狗，自己咪又係去做金融狗。。。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br /